  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Fast track programs, multimodal therapy strategies, have been introduced in many surgical
      fields to minimize postoperative morbidity and mortality. This study is intended to evaluate
      a rehabilitation program in comparison with a historical series.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
